Neural Networks, Exemplar-based Generalization

Explanation: 
The paper investigates the generalization capabilities of backpropagation learning in feed-forward and recurrent feed-forward connectionist networks, which are types of neural networks. Additionally, the paper compares the results to an exemplar-based generalization scheme, which is a type of case-based reasoning. Therefore, the paper belongs to the sub-categories of Neural Networks and Case Based.
